#. Tag: interface
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Bar"
msgstr "Barra de menús"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <interface>Menu Bar</interface> contains several choices of drop-down "
"menus. These are <guimenu>Game</guimenu>, <guimenu>Move</guimenu>, "
"<guimenu>View</guimenu>, <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and <guimenu>Help</"
"guimenu>. Click with the &LMB; or <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>the underlined letter</keycap></keycombo> to show the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"La <interface>Barra de menús</interface> conté diverses opcions en menús "
"desplegables. Aquests són <guimenu>Joc</guimenu>, <guimenu>Mou</guimenu>, "
"<guimenu>Visualitza</guimenu>, <guimenu>Arranjament</guimenu> i "
"<guimenu>Ajuda</guimenu>. Feu clic amb el &BER; o <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Alt;<keycap>la lletra subratllada</keycap></keycombo> per a mostrar el "
"menú desplegable."

#. Tag: interface
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toolbar"
msgstr "Barra d'eines"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Provides the player with icon shortcuts for commonly used actions. These are "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-new.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>New</guiicon>, "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-undo.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Undo</guiicon>, "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"games-hint.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Hint</guiicon>, "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"actions-lastmoves.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Show Last Move</"
"guiicon>, and <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"actions-"
"legalmoves.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"<guiicon>Show Legal Moves</guiicon>. Place the mouse pointer over any of "
"these icons and click with the &LMB; to activate."
msgstr ""
"Proporciona al jugador les dreceres d'icona per a les accions d'ús comú. "
"Aquestes són <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-"
"new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Nova</"
"guiicon>, <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-undo.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Desfés</"
"guiicon>, <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"games-hint.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Consell</"
"guiicon>, <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"actions-"
"lastmoves.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"<guiicon>Mostra l'últim moviment</guiicon> i "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"actions-legalmoves.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Mostra els "
"moviments legals</guiicon>. Col·loqueu el punter del ratolí a sobre de "
"qualsevol d'aquestes icones i feu clic amb el &BER; per a activar-la."

